          GOTO      MODB0100
.
.         Change items
.
MODB2000  CALL      MCHG0000
          GOTO      MODB0100
.
.         Delete items
.
MODB3000  CALL      MDEL0000
          GOTO      MODB0100
.
.         Redisplay screen
.
MODB4000  MOVE      ZERO,MSKIPASK            * Stop display at every screen
          CALL      DISB0000
          GOTO      MODB0100
.
.         Exit without posting
.
MODB5000  COMPARE   ZERO,RCPCHG
