          MOVE      RBREG,VREGISTR
          MOVE      RBINV,VINVOICE
          MOVE      RBAMT,VAMOUNT
          MOVE      RBPERDSC,VPERDISC
          MOVE      RBDISC,VDISCAMT
.
          CALL      CHGF4000                 * Change AMOUNT
          CALL      CHGF5000                 * Change DISCOUNT PERCENTAGE
