          CALL      DETMPR1
          CALL      MAXP0000                 * Recalculate MMAXPAGE & MMAXTRAN
          MOVE      ONE,MSKIPASK             * Display till required screen
          CALL      DISB0000
          GOTO      MDEL0000
.
